{# Character profile block for Writer templates.
   Provides character personality context for dialogue writing.
   Identity/costume tags are injected automatically by PromptBuilder — Gemini should NOT generate them.
   Expects: ctx (character_context or character_b_context), speaker ("A", "B", or None for monologue) #}
{% if speaker %}SPEAKER {{ speaker }} - {% endif %}CHARACTER PROFILE:
Character Name: {{ ctx.name }}
Gender: {{ ctx.gender }}
{%- if ctx.description %}
Personality/Background: {{ ctx.description }}
{%- endif %}
{%- if ctx.costume_tags | length > 0 %}
Costume Reference (for script context only — do NOT include in image_prompt):
{{ ctx.costume_tags | join(', ') }}
{%- endif %}

⚠️ SCRIPT RULES for {{ ctx.name }}:
- Write dialogue/narration that matches {{ ctx.gender }} character's natural speech patterns
{%- if ctx.description %}
- Reflect this character's personality: {{ ctx.description }}
{%- endif %}
- The character's gender and personality MUST be consistent across ALL scenes
